  "text": "The conclusions by [CITATION_1] are also relevant for the present study. Open-walled, \"locally periodic Michell-like frame microstructures\" are not optimal with respect to stiffness. If one allows plate-like microstructures, much stiffer material structures are achieved. The theoretically achievable stiffness improvements are studied for 2D and 3D microstructures in the following.",
